  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Delete Statement - External Securities Account</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page concept  - topic-topic concept-concept \" id=\"loiobd6222c735fd490aac345359b4ecc935\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Delete Statement - External Securities Account</h1><div class=\"body conbody\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">App ID:</span>\n<span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">RECON6</span></p>\n<div class=\"section section_pfdb use\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"loiobd6222c735fd490aac345359b4ecc935__ESAS_DELETE\">With this app, you can delete external securities account\nstatements, for example, after reconciliation with the internal securities account\nclass positions. </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2>\n\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"loiobd6222c735fd490aac345359b4ecc935__ol_w44_bzj_ctb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Open the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete Statement - External Securities\nAccount</span> app on the SAP Fiori launchpad.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Using the selection criteria, you can select the external securities account\nstatements that you want to delete. For example, you could select all\nexternal securities account statements with the status\n<span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">SCLOS</span>.</p><p class=\"p\">To calculate the market values in local currency, you can choose the\nsecurities stock exchange and the security price type that you want to\nuse.</p><aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\">You can first delete external securities account statements as a\n<span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">test run</span>.</p></aside></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span>.</p></li>\n</ol>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"loiobd6222c735fd490aac345359b4ecc935__section_uwl_zbn_dtb\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Supported Device Types\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Supported Device Types</h2>\n\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"loiobd6222c735fd490aac345359b4ecc935__d299e1129\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Desktop</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Tablet</p></li>\n</ul>\n</section></div>\n</div><div class=\"related-links\"> <div class=\"relinfo\"><div class=\"relinfotitle \">Related Information</div><div><a class=\"link\" href=\"4a8fd27cebe03897e10000000a42189c.html\">External Securities Account Statements</a></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
